{
  "text": "These were also carried out by the orthopaedic surgeons at the time of the ultrasound examination. Examination by ultrasound was usually done on the third day after birth by the orthopaedic surgeons who were involved in the study (TT, AT, TB, KJH). The ultrasound method described by Terjesen et al [CITATION_1] and Holen et al 14 was",
